	<h1 class="title">猫眼独立运营，它离真正的互联网电影公司还有多远？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">彭卡茜 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-12 06:35:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25294/medium/25294.jpg?1460372129" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="25294" data-title="《猫眼独立运营，它离真正的互联网电影公司还有多远？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25294/medium/25294.jpg?1460372129" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25294.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
